Gain experience in multiple aspects of HR including;
 Onboarding and offboarding of staff
 Record keeping &amp; leave administration
 Involvement in staff welfare programs
 Other ad-hoc HR projects

Trainee to be involved in:
1. Maintaining of HR records
2. Handling of electronic leave administration
3. Planning and organizing for staff welfare programs (e.g. lunch talks &amp; CSR)
4. HR statistics &amp; reports
5. Staff onboarding &amp; offboarding
6. Ad-hoc HR projects

Technical Skills and Competencies Trainee will learn:
1. How to engage and communicate with team members and stakeholders professionally;
2. Project management
3. Record keeping
4. Sensitivity &amp; maintaining of confidentiality
5. Presentation skills
6. Multitasking &amp; Time Management

